                ))}
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-sm md:text-lg">Excellent Garden Maintenance</h3>
                <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-gray-600">Garden Maintenance - Northampton</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 italic mb-2 md:mb-4 text-sm md:text-base">
              "Very professional service. They transformed our overgrown garden and now maintain it regularly. Always on time and tidy work. Highly recommend!"
            </p>
            <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-gray-600">— Zachery B., Northampton</p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Review 2 -->
          <div class="bg-white p-4 md:p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md border border-light-green/20">
