                ))}
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-sm md:text-lg">Fantastic Clearance Service</h3>
                <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-gray-600">House Clearance - Kettering</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 italic mb-2 md:mb-4 text-sm md:text-base">
              "Needed a full garage clearance and they made it so easy. Fair price, arrived when they said they would, and cleared everything quickly. Very pleased."
            </p>
